{"tid":1964196,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★美國疫情重災區紐約有逾2200警員確診","createTime":"2020-04-08T15:39:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T16:18:47.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7465af89f6c2faa05bd875c4916a71d22d1c7296","tid":1964196,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）在美國肆虐美國，紐約市更是疫情重災區。紐約市警察局（NYPD）4月6日發表的報告顯示，確診感染新型冠狀病毒的警務人員有逾2200人，又有6974名制服警員生病，佔總數19.3%，意味每5名警員就有1人感到不適。<br />\n<br />\n報告又顯示，至今確診新冠肺炎的警員人數多達2228人，當中12人死亡。紐約市警察局長謝伊（Dermot Shea）曾表示，有必要時會實施12小時輪班制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/458732/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%89%E9%80%BE2200%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F458732%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2596%25AB%25E6%2583%2585%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2581%25BD%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%25E6%259C%2589%25E9%2580%25BE2200%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbuTimN4xbKJd0qqIWjmG9ok%3D&h=b232bfe7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/458732/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E9%87%8D%E7%81%BD%E5%8D%80%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E6%9C%89%E9%80%BE2200%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA</a>"},{"pid":"a7a62a6d7c9c3ce1f54451ce48e7fd8190c9108b","tid":1964196,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T15:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><